description.narrative: The project development objective is to improve the efficiency of the paved municipal road network. Efficiency will be improved as a result of improvements to the institutional framework used by the Borrower in four key areas to deliver adequate transport conditions to users (planning, environmental licensing, participation of private sector, and execution), combined with improvements in the condition of the paved municipal road network.
